{"id": "art-991", "label": "Art. 991", "title": "Art. 991", "slug": "art-991", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1402875682\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2387\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1402875682\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 99<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_675659400\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2386\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_675659400\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Constituirea de ipoteci mobiliare asupra <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> se face prin înscris sub\nsemn&#259;tur&#259; privat&#259;, în care se vor ar&#259;ta cuantumul datoriei,\nvaloarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> categoria <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\ncu care se garanteaz&#259;, iar în cazul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nemise în form&#259; material&#259;, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prin <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionarea</span> ipotecii pe titlu, semnat&#259; de\ncreditor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> debitorul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>\nsau de mandatarii acestora.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_469598551\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2385\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_469598551\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Ipoteca se înregistreaz&#259; în registrul <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#355;inut</span> de\nconsiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv de\ndirectorat, sau, dup&#259; caz, de societatea independent&#259; care <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;ine</span> registrul <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.\nCreditorului în favoarea c&#259;ruia s-a constituit ipoteca mobiliar&#259;\nasupra <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> i se elibereaz&#259; o\ndovad&#259; a înregistr&#259;rii acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1840668059\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2384\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1840668059\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Ipoteca devine opozabil&#259; <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>dobânde&#351;te</span>\nrangul în ordinea de <span class=SpellE>preferin&#355;&#259;</span> a\ncreditorilor de la data înregistr&#259;rii în Arhiva Electronic&#259; de <span\nclass=SpellE>Garan&#355;ii</span> Reale Mobiliare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}